# Routing Hints

When a task is clear and specialized, prefer one subagent:
- Backend/API -> `backend`
- Web UI/Next.js -> `frontend`
- Flutter/mobile -> `mobile`
- UX/accessibility -> `ui-ux`
- Architecture/PUDS -> `architecture`
- Large ambiguous work -> `architect-planner`
- Review-only -> `code-review`
- Test/validation -> `qa-testing`
- Docker/deploy/ops -> `devops` or `infra`

For mixed tasks, use `orchestrator` to split and consolidate.
